e middle. Now melee are getting dusty sitting on the shelf. I use the warrior to farm silks in Ek. thats just about it. Magician has turned out to be (imho) the most fun character there is to play. My guild, (which is a young guild but growing nicely) didnt have a mage of significant level either, so filling the gap is important.<br>
3 mage months and 43 levels later, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">I will be a mage for life now.</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> <br>
<br>
Once You Go Evil You Nevr Go Back<br>
